ed="T" n="0718b18"/><persName key="A000780">釋無極高</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000048208">中印度</placeName>人，<name>梵</name>云<persName key="A000780">阿地瞿多</persName>，<name>華</name>云<lb
ed="T" n="0718b19"/><persName key="A000780">無極高</persName>也。出家氏族未憑書之。<persName key="A000780">高</persName>學窮滿<lb
ed="T" n="0718b20"/>字，行潔圓珠，精練五明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g88"/>，妙通三藏。<date from-iso="+0652-02-18" key="j19592461959274" to-iso="+0652-03-17"><name>永徽</name>三<lb
ed="T" n="0718b21"/>年壬子歲正月</date>，自<placeName key="PL000000055425">西印度</placeName>齎<name>梵</name>夾來屆<placeName key="PL000000042189">長<lb
ed="T" n="0718b22"/>安</placeName>，勅令<placeName key="PL000000042293">慈門寺</placeName><ptr target="#n329"/>安置。沙門<persName key="A000827">大乘琮</persName>等十六人、<lb
ed="T" n="0718b23"/><persName key="A005857">英公李世勣</persName>、<persName key="A008937">鄂公尉遲<supplied>敬</supplied>德</persName><ptr target="#n479"/>等十二人，同請<persName key="A000780">高</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0718b24"/>於<placeName key="PL000000042132">慧日寺浮圖院</placeName>建陀羅尼普集會壇，所須<lb
ed="T" n="0718b25"/>供辦<ptr rend="display:none;" target="#n330"/>。法成之日，屢現靈異，<ref target="#PL000000042189" type="place">京</ref>中道俗咸歎希<lb
ed="T" n="0718b26"/>逢。沙門<persName key="A008889">玄楷</persName>等固請翻其法本。以<date from-iso="+0653-02-06" key="j19596001960338" to-iso="+0655-02-14">四年癸<lb
ed="T" n="0718b27"/>丑至于五年</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000042131">慧日寺</placeName>從《金剛大道場經》<ptr target="#n88"/><lb
ed="T" n="0718b28"/>中撮要而譯，集成一部，名《陀羅尼集經》<ptr target="#n90"/>一<lb
ed="T" n="0718b29"/>十二卷，<persName key="A008889">玄楷</persName>筆受<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g53"/>。于時有<placeName key="PL000000048247">中印度大菩提寺</placeName><pb ed="T" n="0718c" xml:id="T50.2061.0718c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0718c01"/><persName key="A000783">阿難律木叉師</persName>、<persName key="A008938">迦葉師</persName>等，於<placeName key="PL000000042312">經行寺</placeName>譯《功德<lb
ed="T" n="0718c02"/>天法》，編在《集經》第十卷內，故不別出焉。</p>
